BIC: Boogerman explodes.

OOC: It wasn't a good game anyway. Anyw=
ay, here I am, back once more. Crawling back has become typical of me. Well=
, this time I'm back for a few reasons. They are below if any of you want t=
o read. I doubt you do, but this is my post and I will type what I want to.=


1: nWo is 4 life.

2: Azure wrote me this pretty little letter and cheere=
d me up.

3: Rudra didn't respond to my teasing RPG posts and I wasn't havi=
ng fun anymore.

4: Cardhead didn't reply to the Boogerman post. Thanks, bu=
ddy!

5: Saliva's "Always" is awesome. That's not a reason, but I believe i=
t to be fact.

6: This RPG can't live without me. Don't say it can, because=
 I like to think it can't. Shut up.

7: Wrestlers shouldn't get so mad. If =
I got any madder I'd be like HHH, and that's definitely not a good thing. I=
 have to make it to reason 8 I can say I have a Megaman total. (GEEK ALERT)=


8: I like wasting the time of the innocent with worthless posts like thes=
e. Yeah, I wasted your time if you read down this far. Oh, not quite. There=
's a reward for your patience provided you did not click delete as you read=
 this. It's 1 million dollars plus a bomb. Oh, never mind. I'm sorry, peopl=
e, this post was my cry for attention! It's because I don't know how to say=
 that NBW is part of who I am now, despite all of the random outbursts of r=
age. Oops, I guess I just did. I'm high on no-sleep right now, forgive this=
 shit. Thanks.

Mr. Mister Zeeryo
